1. "*Stolicu* je trebalo da preuredi u kancelariji." (The chair had to be rearranged in the office.)
2. "Ona je lako pomerila *stolicu* u kutu sobe." (She easily moved the chair to the corner of the room.)
3. "On je postavio *stolicu* ispred prozora." (He put the chair in front of the window.)
4. "Ona je uzela *stolicu* i sjela za stol." (She took the chair and sat down at the table.)
5. "On je podigao *stolicu* i postavio je na stranu." (He lifted the chair and put it aside.)
6. "On je pokrio *stolicu* mekom krpom." (He covered the chair with a soft cloth.)